  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy a continental buffet with fresh fruit, pastries, breads, cereals, juices, teas and coffee is served each morning. Half board and full board are available for a supplement and offer a buffet service. Those choosing full board can enjoy a menu service lunch with buffet starter.</p>
<p>The hotel's restaurant is in a panoramic position overlooking the sea, They serve a selection of local cuisine as well as international dishes. A relaxed bar serves drinks and snacks throughout the day and the Piano bar is open from April to early October with aperitivi and evening entertainment six times a week. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
