  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><u>Pool &amp; Beach</u></strong></p>
<p>Relax in the hotel's charming outdoor pool with sun loungers and great views to admire. There's also a dedicated children's pool. </p>
<p>The private beach is normally open from April to the end of October. It is a natural beach of sand and pebbles where there are parasols and sun chairs for guests to relax on. Beach towels can be rented (approx. €5)</p>
<p><strong><u>Genera Facilities</u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Tennis</li>
<li>Ping Pong</li>
<li>Football</li>
<li>Animation programme</li>
<li>Mini club for 4-12 year old’s (19 Jun - 11 September)</li>
<li>Children's Playground</li>
<li>Free WiFi in common areas</li>
<li>Parking</li>
<li>Return shuttle to Tropea (approx. €10pp)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
