  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Villaggio Baia d’Ercole is right on one of the most stunning coastlines in Calabria - expect sandy beaches and incredible clear water. They've got a lovely pool and great restaurant with panoramic sea views. It's a nice escape here with simple, traditional rooms and a real authentic feel.</p>]]></listingDescription>
