  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are about 14-16m² sleep up to three people. These rooms are decorated in a modern style and have been completely renovated. They are located in front of the pool and have a terrace or balcony. All rooms have a TV, air conditioning, safe and hairdryer. Baby cots are available on request, free of charge.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> range from 14-20m², sleep up to four people and have a balcony or terrace. They're simply furnished and have a double bed - the third and fourth bed are bunk beds. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Family Apartments </strong>are about 20-30m² sleep up to five people. These apartments have two rooms, a bathroom and a balcony or terrace. They're available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Double Rooms for Single Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
